                                    padding-top: 2pt;
                                    padding-left: 2pt;
                                    padding-right: 21pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: justify;
                                ">
                            Is the seafarer free from any medical condition
                            likely to be aggravated by service at sea or to
                            render the seafarer unfit for such service or to
                            endanger the health of other persons on board?
                            <i>Yes/No</i>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="height: 19pt">
                    <td style="width: 25pt">
                        <p style="text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left">
                            <br />
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="width: 44pt">
                        <p class="s6" style="
                                    padding-top: 2pt;
                                    padding-left: 16pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: left;
                                ">
                            3.9.
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="width: 360pt">
                        <p class="s6" style="
                                    padding-top: 2pt;
                                    padding-left: 2pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: left;
                                ">
                            Date of examination: <i>(day/month/year)</i>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="height: 25pt">
                    <td style="width: 25pt">
                        <p style="text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left">
                            <br />
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="width: 44pt">
                        <p class="s6" style="
                                    padding-top: 2pt;
                                    padding-left: 16pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: left;
                                ">
                            3.10.
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="width: 360pt">
                        <p class="s6" style="
                                    padding-top: 2pt;
                                    padding-left: 2pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: left;
                                ">
                            Expiry date of certificate:
                            <i>(day/month/year)</i>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="height: 25pt">
                    <td style="width: 25pt">
                        <p class="s6" style="
                                    padding-top: 8pt;
                                    padding-left: 2pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: left;
                                ">
                            4
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="width: 404pt" colspan="2">
                        <p class="s7" style="
                                    padding-top: 9pt;
                                    padding-left: 16pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: left;
                                ">
                            Details of the issuing authority
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="height: 19pt">
                    <td style="width: 25pt">
                        <p style="text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left">
                            <br />
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="width: 44pt">
                        <p class="s6" style="
                                    padding-top: 2pt;
                                    padding-left: 16pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: left;
                                ">
                            4.1.
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="width: 360pt">
                        <p class="s6" style="
                                    padding-top: 2pt;
                                    padding-left: 2pt;
                                    text-indent: 0pt;
                                    text-align: left;
                                ">
                            Official stamp (including name) of the issuing
                            authority
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="height: 16pt">
                    <td style="width: 25pt">
                        <p style="text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left">
                            <br />
