                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                Notes:
            </h3>
            <p class="s18" style="
                        padding-left: 43pt;
                        text-indent: 0pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                1<span class="s19">
                    Values given in Snellen decimal notation.</span>
            </p>
            <p class="s18" style="
                        padding-left: 69pt;
                        text-indent: -25pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                2<span class="s19">
                    A value of at least 0.7 in one eye is recommended to
                    reduce the risk of undetected underlying eye
                    disease.</span>
            </p>
            <p class="s19" style="
                        padding-left: 69pt;
                        text-indent: -25pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                <span class="s18">3</span> As defined in the
                <i>International Recommendations for Colour Vision
                    Requirements for Transport </i>by the Commission Internationale de l&#39;Eclairage
                (CIE-143-2001, including any subsequent versions).
            </p>
            <p class="s18" style="
                        padding-left: 43pt;
                        text-indent: 0pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                4<span class="s19">
                    Subject to assessment by a clinical vision specialist
                    where indicated by initial examination findings.</span>
            </p>
            <p class="s18" style="
                        padding-left: 43pt;
                        text-indent: 0pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                5<span class="s19">
                    Engine department personnel shall have a combined
                    eyesight vision of at least 0.4.</span>
            </p>
            <p class="s18" style="
                        padding-top: 1pt;
                        padding-left: 43pt;
                        text-indent: 0pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                6<span class="s19">
                    CIE colour vision standard 1 or 2.</span>
            </p>
            <p class="s18" style="
                        padding-top: 1pt;
                        padding-left: 43pt;
                        text-indent: 0pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                7<span class="s19">
                    CIE colour vision standard 1, 2 or 3.</span>
            </p>
            <p style="text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left"><br /></p>
            <p class="s10" style="
