            </p>
            <p style="text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left"><br /></p>
            <h3 style="
                        padding-left: 40pt;
                        text-indent: 0pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
                Guidance regarding medical standards
            </h3>
            <p style="text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left"><br /></p>
            <p class="s11" style="
                        padding-left: 40pt;
                        text-indent: 0pt;
                        text-align: left;
                    ">
